      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine starts and runs consistently, but you may notice some typical high-mileage vibrations and minor oil seepage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some fading paint on the roof, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear and a few small tears. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character and the need for upcoming routine maintenance.",
