    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014it runs smoothly and still looks great parked in the driveway! It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something reliable and well-loved that\u2019s ready for many more adventures. I've taken good care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to chat or come take a look!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example has been fastidiously maintained with the critical Big Three addressed: the rear subframe has been reinforced, the VANOS system overhauled, and rod bearings replaced. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for precise turn-in. While the Estoril Blue finish shows light road wear, the drivetrain is robust, delivering power through a Getrag 6-speed manual and a functional M-Variable differential lock. A true driver's spec for those prioritizing mechanical pedigree over concours perfection.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
