    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sports sedan strikes the perfect balance between raw performance and daily drivability. Finished in a timeless Metallic Silver, the exterior retains a deep gloss, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia speak to its enjoyed history on the open road. Inside, the premium black leather seats show light, natural bolster wear consistent with careful use, while the dashboard and electronics remain in excellent working order. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust; it has benefited from a recent comprehensive service, including fresh fluids and a new set of high-performance tires. The engine pulls strongly through every gear, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. Complete with a documented service history and two sets of keys, this car is ready for its next enthusiast owner who values a well-cared-for machine.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
